ike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:49:57.000Z","msg":"這個分析很透徹, 香港人現在跪下也不會有活路。<br />\n停止反抗黑警就會變返白嗎? <br />\n停止反抗只會換來更多的不公義, 更多的濫捕和更強的報復。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:31:40.000Z","msg":"冇錯，支共嘅報復心極重<br />\n睇歷史都一堆<br />\n反右、三反五反<br />\n最近嘅烏坎都係最佳例子<br />\n<br />\n所以，一係唔好打，要打就要打殘佢<br />\n<br />\nTrump唔可以俾佢拖<br />\n而係要一下子拖垮強國<br />\n有如當年英國佬對清朝一樣<br />\n冇好處都唔好停"},{"pid":"bab4222d86a077b2aea535034b972f7618db7092","tid":1643441,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d0eca519f83f95fde1ef73ed713dfa189ea0065","tid":1643441,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e11392e023fdf94dc5a164ca4ccfe7c3a876524d","tid":1643441,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"381473551dc3c357fb41f23be5fc47a73d2b9de1","tid":1643441,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:54:45.000Z","msg":"呼籲回歸選舉，停止一切街頭行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:46:38.000Z","msg":"因為依家叫大家收手果班根本都係既得利益者或上左岸既人  佢地只想<br />\n香港回復番幾個月前既狀態 <br />\n就算香港之後變成點都差都好 佢地都可以隨時拍拍囉柚移民走人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:33:10.000Z","msg":"要整死呢班人唔難<br />\n金融機構都係春袋<br />\n不過有左膠手軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b414401818abb9ea7657623d0e6d9fb6c8b82b2","tid":1643441,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"佢可唔可以返香港教書<br />\n想sit堂"},{"pid":"272d791cfd53442f767df6459bc8816f46df6b0c","tid":1643441,"uid":110517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:37:07.000Z","msg":"孔誥烽，知我所想宣我昐望"},{"pid":"7d3608ba836a33f856cea5e49ea09a1120304447","tid":1643441,"uid":82588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:40:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a6b94938dd4df069959ea0867222ad69ae0ddce","tid":1643441,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:52:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a056a1cfad07d078cfcda0519b079f216a584e84","tid":1643441,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"所謂的「攬炒派」，其實很會計算，很理性，絕非情緒化和亂來。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc6349bb5cb6997ee41cd550c786c40fe154eb3","tid":1643441,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cc6e64a3588b866a325ea57a17b87183d907ad3","tid":1643441,"uid":2883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:01:21.000Z","msg":"班休息撚根本駁唔到，剩係不斷loop幾個白痴理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c4cba795b4ccc65c463b75b21ea554a9ef6396","tid":1643441,"uid":260677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b47f85f27520c7c423d03632111cc4de254a064","tid":1643441,"uid":28114,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"現在抗爭者中間普遍有「攬炒」（玉石俱焚）傾向，就是因為不少抗爭者判斷，若現在止戰，香港便會陷入（一）的境地。若繼續抗爭，迫使北京用更極端的方式應對，便可能造成（二）或（三）的結果。從他們的角度看，（一）是輸，（三）是贏，（二）是打和。所謂的「攬炒派」，其實很會計算，很理性，絕非情緒化和亂來。<br />\n<br />\n八月五日的三罷和抗爭升級後，林鄭和國務院放狠話說香港抗爭者是港獨，「光復香港 時代革命」口號是港獨口號。當時很多看似開明派空群勸抗爭者軟化，停叫光復口號以免刺激中共，不然後果不堪設想。最後抗爭者沒有理會，繼續升級，口號繼續叫，還作了歌。最後解放軍還是沒有出來，北京反而容許林鄭宣布正式撤回送中條例。<br />\n<br />\n現在政府動用緊急權力反蒙面，看似開明派又說抗議者不要中計升級，反而應該休兵。決心要避免（一），豁出去要爭取（二）或（三）的前線抗爭者會不會聽，大家心裡有數。那些苦口婆心說要避免悲劇的社會賢達，與其浪費時間說服抗爭者接受（一），不如試試說服你們相熟的上層精英接受（三），還比較實際。<br />\n<br />\n- 孔誥烽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/commentaries/dcwatcher/DCWatcher-10092019080634.html?encoding=traditional\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fcommentaries%2Fdcwatcher%2FDCWatcher-10092019080634.html%3Fencoding%3Dtraditional&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=be271085\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/commentaries/dcwatcher/DCWatcher-10092019080634.html?encoding=traditional</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:20:10.000Z","msg":"救命分析得好好<em><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em>"},{"pid":"a60d93c220ee4cc4d57d94129b2c67b16c27bf16","tid":1643441,"uid":47555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}